+# Exploration 002: Tao Filter for the Harmonic Far-Field Pressure Loophole
+
+## Goal
+
+Decide whether the mission's surviving harmonic far-field pressure loophole is **Tao-compatible**, **Tao-incompatible**, or **still unclear**.
+
