+| Near/far split with harmonic far-field on `Q_k` | Yes, in principle | Not preserved in a clean local form after multiplier averaging | [CHECKED] lost |
+| Harnack-ready harmonic component | Available in the loophole picture | No sourced surviving analogue found | [CHECKED] absent |
+| Overall classification | Loophole can be formulated | Loophole structure is not preserved | `Tao-incompatible` |
+
+## 6. Recommended Next Move
+
