+- Exact obstruction recovered:
+  `I_k ≤ ||P_{k21}||_{L^q} ||d_k||_{L^2} ||1_{v_k>0}||_{L^{2q/(q-2)}}` with
+  `||P_{k21}||_{L^q} ≤ C_q`, `||d_k||_{L^2} ≤ U_{k-1}^{1/2}`, and `||1_{v_k>0}|| ≤ C^k U_{k-1}^{5(q-2)/(6q)}`, giving
